        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Smarter Pretrial Detention for Drug Charges Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill removes the presumption of pretrial detention for an individual who is charged with a federal drug offense for which the maximum term of imprisonment is 10 years or more. </p>]]></text>
